# This app runs on PostgreSQL. Set DATABASE_URL to a real Postgres connection
# string before running `npm run dev`, `prisma migrate`, or `prisma db seed`
# — there is no local-file fallback anymore. A free Neon (neon.tech) or
# Vercel Postgres database works fine for both local dev and deployment.
#
# SESSION_SECRET below is a demo value with no real secrecy value — it's
# committed to the repo, so anyone with read access to this history could
# forge a session cookie. Generate a fresh one (`openssl rand -base64 32`)
# and set it as an environment variable in your hosting provider (not in
# this file) before any real deployment.
DATABASE_URL=""
SESSION_SECRET="avIatUCpwbOt7NsM/uwNmaUkUE3byDtnk7RPFZ5m9jA="
